# Trashify Image Datasets
This is the datasets for classification of trash types with Machine Learning using MobileNet V2 model on Sipeed Maix Go board. This datasets contain 356 pictures of trashes in three category (metal, paper, and plastic).
Visit the [repository](https://github.com/iotub/trashify) for source code of trash classification with Sipeed Maix Go.
